OL,3,CTemperatures to drop after hottest day
OL,4,Cof the year
OL,6,FClouds and cooler weather will return
OL,7,Fthis weekend after the UK experienced
OL,8,Fthe hottest day of the year so far on
OL,9,FFriday, the Met Office has said.
OL,11,FThe mercury reached 31.9C at St James'
OL,12,FPark, central London, making Friday
OL,13,Fthe warmest recorded day of 2024.
OL,15,FThe AA advised routes to the coast
OL,16,Fwill be far busier than usual this
OL,17,Fweekend as families flock to take
OL,18,Fadvantage of the hot weather.
