OL,6,FBrighton and Bournemouth, on the south
OL,7,Fcoast, have already experienced
OL,8,Fheavier traffic because of day-
OL,9,Ftrippers, it added.
OL,11,FHowever, temperatures are unlikely to
OL,12,Freach the high 20Cs for "at least a
OL,13,Fweek or so" now, a Met Office
OL,14,Fforecaster said.
OL,16,FClouds will return on Saturday and
OL,17,Fhigher temperatures will be restricted
OL,18,Fto the east and south east of England,
OL,19,Fwhich could still see 28-29C.
