OL,6,FHe said it is too early to tell if the
OL,7,Fmercury will top Friday's reading, but
OL,8,F"I certainly wouldn't rule out a
OL,9,Fhigher temperature in August or even
OL,10,Flater this month".
OL,12,FThere will be "occasional very warm or
OL,13,Fhot spells" in August but there is "no
OL,14,Fstrong signal" that high temperatures
OL,15,Fwill be prolonged or widespread across
OL,16,Fthe UK, he added.
OL,18,FEast and south-east England have
OL,19,Falready seen "almost double" the
OL,20,Frainfall expected for the whole of
OL,21,FJuly, Mr Morgan said.
