OL,6,F"I think that's why a lot of people
OL,7,Fhave welcomed the last couple of days,
OL,8,Fbut Scotland and Northern Ireland have
OL,9,Fnot see the high temperatures that the
OL,10,Frest of the UK have seen ` they're
OL,11,Fstill waiting if they do like hot
OL,12,Fweather."
OL,14,FThe AA recommended that road users
OL,15,Ftravelling in the heat put a sun
OL,16,Fshield over the back windows, have
OL,17,Ficed water in the car, try to leave
OL,18,Ftheir vehicles in the shade and use a
OL,19,Fwindscreen shade when parked.
