OL,6,FOn Thursday, the Health and Safety
OL,7,FAuthority (HSA) urged employees to
OL,8,Fprotect themselves from ultraviolet
OL,9,F(UV) radiation.
OL,11,FIt suggested employers conduct a risk
OL,12,Fassessment for "potential UV hazards",
OL,13,Fencourage breaks, and that staff wear
OL,14,Fclothing such as wide-brimmed hats to
OL,15,Fprotect them from the Sun.
